Name:           heimer
Version:        3.6.4
Release:        0
Summary:        Mind map, diagram, and note-taking tool
License:        CC-BY-SA-3.0 AND GPL-3.0-only
Group:          Productivity/Office/Other
URL:            https://github.com/juzzlin/Heimer
